{"tid":2499271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果自己老竇食軟飯，大家會唔會睇唔起自己老竇","createTime":"2021-04-21T18:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T19:34:16.000Z","uid":227776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4bad1ada12317b67e37be6b6c9e665fc07a221","tid":2499271,"uid":227776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T18:22:12.000Z","msg":"我阿爸因為隻腳有少少問題，所以長期行動不便<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以係我小三嘅時候就失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住變咗我老母出去做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係基本上由小三開始就冇照顧過我。放學就去補習社。差唔多九點幾先返唔到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住由中一開始早午晚三餐佢就咁比$40我自己搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到我16歲的時候我開始返兼職，叫識咗少少人，諗住介紹份聽電話嘅工俾佢，因為唔使行嚟行去<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩仲話而家呢一代嘅男人冇用，淨係識得出去搞搞震。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d1f85f35c230a5b88826544739d0f6160887c7","tid":2499271,"uid":190187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T19:20:26.000Z","msg":"身體呢啲唔係自己可以控制<br />\n加上而家女權盛行 女人養男人有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622378ba9ffef596b8967fe997020020d1bdb624","tid":2499271,"uid":341722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T19:29:10.000Z","msg":"咁佢有無返份工<br />\n唔做野唔係問題 態度先係"},{"pid":"a5bda61bb605f276cfb61cfbba85eb688b97970c","tid":2499271,"uid":48162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T19:31:57.000Z","msg":"由細到大嘅志願就係食軟飯"},{"pid":"79c839a882cc253e5eeb6681024283b733c0071b","tid":2499271,"uid":148017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T19:33:53.000Z","msg":"憑自己實力食軟飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2ed12ff95f227d86135ee1b0ed9652999785f3","tid":2499271,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T19:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有乜睇唔睇得起<br />\n話哂都係一家人<br />\n你老豆唔做嘢爛賭就話睇唔起姐<br />\n你老母都唔嫌棄 幾時先輪撚到你"}]}